Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}圣天空战记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要坠入爱河每个人都会变得如此孤单?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正拥抱着比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切必定都是为了让我俩能绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用泪水来呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你早就给了我 最宝贵的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我的幻觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.09,0:01:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是阿斯多利亚王国的边陲地带
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里的森林遇见了光之天使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字叫亚连·歇萨尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当他的巨人打赢了艾斯嘉科尼时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了不祥的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她又…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳，你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连，你快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快带着大家逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不见的敌人会来攻击这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.10,0:02:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来人型装甲的战斗\N给你带来了太大的刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的会烧起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的一切都会被火焰包围
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔性的美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击法尼利亚的那个看不见的巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将一切都给烧毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在胡说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女孩怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女孩听说是从幻之月来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说幻之月会招来灾祸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:02:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这座城会发生什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住□
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亚的士兵不准被迷信冲昏了头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为我部下的无礼向你致歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是累了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回房休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.49,0:03:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？德欧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在森林里抓到一个可疑的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑的家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成那女孩所说的话是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大，我把她带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:03:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们认识吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是法尼利亚的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于见到您了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露，法尼利亚的情况怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都…全都烧掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城里的武士们全都死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存活下来的人也离散到各地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有半个人在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在找
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会烧起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她发高烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵，把那女孩也一起带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙就快消失不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的理想未来已经开始出现动摇了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是让龙就这样逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将无法预测这会为我们的未来产生多少影响
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把龙抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:05:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是出击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道龙在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亚是同盟国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是慢慢等外交交涉那猎物早就溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必要这样把事情闹大？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要穿上你制作的隐形披风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不会韶下是我们寨巴哈帝国所为的证据啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好期待战利品吧，军师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不放心让那些士兵\N来照顾你们这两位女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈她一定很担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的母亲一定是个美人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家母在我小时候就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的，那是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.94,0:07:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错，家母的确是个美人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个喜爱花朵的温柔女性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从某天家妹无故失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那天之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家母就因为伤心过度而卧病在床
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果家妹还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该差不多跟你一样大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不晓得该怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一谈起家人，我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明才跟天野学长告白没多久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样是不是真的很随便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这粒种子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去下马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到城里去巡视一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…请你小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人真的已经来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么事情，我都会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是国王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑到这种地下牢房来\N是来妨碍我睡午觉的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你这种森林居民身上\N应该带有格拉尔的叶子吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会知道这种叶子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我王兄告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说它可以中和大部分的毒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地鼠，帮我扶着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.28,0:10:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有够大牌的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到连队长都跟着迷信起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:11:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在的非常戒备状态啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意那个幻之月女孩所说的话，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在意的是那个迪兰度的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的眼睛散发出渴望鲜血的疯狂凶光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道寨巴哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会对我们发动攻击吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会停靠在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就表示他们知道艾斯嘉科尼就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦发动攻击他们一定会赶尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的会这么狠吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他们就会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不韶活□也就不会韶下证据
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.34,0:11:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把库鲁杰特准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧，里殿\N好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候要动手，迪兰度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机继续待命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不陪你们玩捉迷藏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是幻之月来的女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只猫正往我这边看着…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的短发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服也很怪异
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都像只猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那对耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那条尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她的个性能再温驯一点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我睡在长椅上？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像在生气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有东西正往这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑到哪里去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.09,0:13:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把病人放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您为了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,药？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是为了做那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你要干嘛啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:13:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静静的别乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草的毒素经由伤□跑了进去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能退烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不见的巨人来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是看不见的巨人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是幻之月招来的噩运
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，是寨巴哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要以谢拉撒特迎敌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼！手无缚鸡之力的人们！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪兰度大人！打开缺口了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！突入！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一切都破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用烟把艾斯嘉科尼给逼出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的寨巴哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇欧，你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大，我真是丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人在什么地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是从地下通道入侵进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经抵挡不住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经搬上库鲁杰特了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库鲁杰特？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座城已经失守
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候撒退了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要逃？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有…已经有这么多伙伴牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能再让更多人牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样还算是武士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会背对着敌人逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了替法尼利亚的人民报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会战到至死方休
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择死亡的匹夫之勇并不是真正的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵，你是法尼利亚王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要王在，人民在，希望也就在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍住这份屈辱才是真正的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士的生命是为了让人们活下去而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点你不要忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇欧，将司令部移至库鲁杰特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传令下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会将你，还有艾斯嘉科尼交给寨巴哈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以亚连·歇萨尔之名发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差这个阀门了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个钟乳洞不会受到影响
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备完毕…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人在哪里？他不在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们马上就会过来会合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收锚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收锚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出航
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧吧，烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.19,0:17:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢至极
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到何时才要停止这种无谓的杀戮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最确实消灭证据的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来只要将被我熏出来的艾斯嘉科尼逮住就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂的阿斯多利亚的亚连\N会因为遭到火攻就乖乖就范吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城的后方有处断崖瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.01,0:18:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说有乌在瀑布之中筑巢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了躲避敌人的攻击…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙在城的后方！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，扬帆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扬帆！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边境的乌合之众还挺有本事的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你们打下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是在漂浮的状态下是无法使用隐形披风的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把看见的人全部解决就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亚的都城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算浮游要塞也追不上这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人型装甲竟然会飞？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:19:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:19:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上方被制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再让你们这些混帐为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身手不错，迪兰度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很强嘛，亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让我开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连，上面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.07,0:20:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭到攻击，舵不受控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为艾斯嘉科尼使得大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士的生命是为了让人们活下去而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵，你打算做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼变成了飞龙？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞龙？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来那就是多伦卡喀大人所说的龙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪，这里交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别走，迪兰度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，追过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人要离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.14,0:21:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是为了让我们逃走，才…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你千万不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.44,0:22:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪斯，请把船调头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去救梵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.67,0:22:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没办法马上调头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帆被弄坏了，舵也不受控制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.12,0:22:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.96,0:22:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.96,0:22:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之风就快来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.80,0:22:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好，乘上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.21,0:22:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好久没猎龙了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.81,0:22:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我来好好玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.19,0:24:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候我早该宰了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.86,0:24:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快，我得快去通知他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.17,0:24:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.30,0:24:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟的刻印
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.09,0:23:14.16,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月儿彼方蓝色探照灯照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:22.61,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降临的天使 你究竟是谁?
